title: June Gloom // Darshan Gooch
description:
The sea speaks to us. She gives spiritual meaning in a world of chaos. She gives reason for spontaneous travel at a moments notice. And she is that wonderful escape for the mind, body and soul. Reef Ambassador Darshan Gooch dances with her, finding synchronicity, balance and meaning, all in the spirit of 'just passing through'.

Video by Adam Warmington
Words: 'The Sea Is My Brother' by Jack Kerouac
Music: Rough Rugged Road Blues, Bumble Bee Slim
